OL,3,CFarmers' 'losing sleep' over
OL,4,Cunpredictable weather
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports journalist Emma
OL,7,FSweeney has been speaking to farmers
OL,8,Fin the North West.
OL,10,FFarmers in the UK say they are "losing
OL,11,Fsleep" over the consequences of an
OL,12,Fincreasingly unpredictable climate on
OL,13,Ftheir crops and livestock.
OL,15,FConsecutive months of heavy rain,
OL,16,Fflooding and soaring prices mean
OL,17,Ffarmers country-wide are facing
OL,18,Funprecedented issues.
