OL,3,CFarmers' 'losing sleep' over
OL,4,Cunpredictable weather
OL,6,FAt the same time, costs of key inputs
OL,7,Flike fertiliser and energy for storing
OL,8,Fcrops like potatoes have remained
OL,9,Fhigh, increasing by 28% over the past
OL,10,Ftwo years.
OL,12,F"We need to be given confidence for
OL,13,Fthe future," Robin explains.
OL,15,F"That confidence can only be given by
OL,16,Fgovernments investing in the
OL,17,Finfrastructure of drainage to make
OL,18,Fsure that the water we do get passes
OL,19,Fout to sea."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
