OL,3,CFarmers' 'losing sleep' over
OL,4,Cunpredictable weather
OL,6,F"The longer we leave it the worse the
OL,7,Fquality will be for the cattle in the
OL,8,Fwinter."
OL,10,FHelen's farm has been in her family
OL,11,Fsince the 1700s and rising costs mean
OL,12,Fthey have had to scale back in recent
OL,13,Fyears.
OL,15,FWithout more help from the government,
OL,16,Fshe feels like problems will go from
OL,17,Fbad to worse.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
