OL,3,CFarmers' 'losing sleep' over
OL,4,Cunpredictable weather
OL,6,FShe said: "At the minute we're just
OL,7,Ftreading water, waiting to see what
OL,8,Fthe government say they want us to do
OL,9,F- environmental scheme wise.
OL,11,F"We're scared to invest in machinery
OL,12,Fand infrastructure because we don't
OL,13,Fknow what kind of funding we will get
OL,14,Fin the future.
OL,16,F"I definitely lose sleep over it. It's
OL,17,Freally hard for a business to live
OL,18,Fwith that level of uncertainty."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
